<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.2">
<l>koṅkuṇ kuḻalār kūṭiyi runtuci rittunīr</l>
<l>iṅkeṉṉi rumiyem pālvanta teṉṟika ḻātamuṉ</l>
<l>tiṅka ḷerikāl ceñcuṭa rāyavaṉ tēcuṭai</l>
<l>naṅkaḷ naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tumeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before those with fragrant curls, gathering and tittering,</l>
<l>Can scold saying, “Why are you coming near us here coughing?”</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship in our effulgent Naṟaiyūr</l>
<l>Of him who became the moon, wind, fire, and the glowing sun.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
